---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About ByteLite - Inventors of Infinite Compression" description="ByteLite LLC: Redefining data storage since 2024. Patent #63/807,027 pending. Learn about our mission to compress infinite data into bytes.">
  <main>
    <section class="hero-section">
      <h1>Redefining Information Theory</h1>
      <p class="lead">ByteLite emerged from a simple question: What if compression isn't about removing redundancy, but transforming representation?</p>
    </section>

    <section class="story-section">
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>Founded in 2024, ByteLite began as an exploration into the mathematical limits of data representation. Through combining advanced mathematics, recursive transformation theory, and hierarchical information storage, we discovered a method to compress data beyond traditional theoretical limits.</p>
      
      <p>Our breakthrough came when we realized that information can exist in multiple dimensions - not just as raw data, but as transformation instructions that can be recursively applied.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="innovation-section">
      <h2>The Innovation</h2>
      <div class="innovation-grid">
        <div class="innovation">
          <h3>Bijective Pairing</h3>
          <p>Mathematical functions that preserve information while transforming representation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="innovation">
          <h3>Recursive Transformation</h3>
          <p>Iterative compression that converges toward minimal representation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="innovation">
          <h3>Hierarchical Storage</h3>
          <p>Information stored as layers of transformation instructions</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="patent-section">
      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>ByteLite's Dynamic Algorithmic Compression technology is protected under U.S. Provisional Patent Application No. 63/807,027, filed May 16, 2025.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="vision-section">
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>We envision a future where data storage limitations become obsolete. Where entire data centers can be backed up to thumb drives. Where interplanetary communication happens in bytes, not gigabytes. Where AI systems can process vastly more information by working with compressed representations.</p>
      
      <p>ByteLite isn't just about compression - it's about reimagining how we think about information itself.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    color: white;
    background: #060813;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00D4FF 0%, #FF006E 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #00D4FF;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .story-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .innovation-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .innovation {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .innovation h3 {
    color: #00D4FF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .patent-section {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vision-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vision-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
